    if not result_file.exists():\n66\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n67\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 0.0\n68\t        scores[\"three_timeframes\"] = 0.0\n69\t        scores[\"monthly_status\"] = 0.0\n70\t        scores[\"three_ma_verified\"] = 0.0\n71\t        return scores\n72\t\n73\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n74\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n75\t\n76\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"none\"]\n77\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n78\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0\n79\t        scores[\"monthly_status\"] = 1.0\n80\t    else:\n81\t        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\d{5}', content))\n82\t        dates = re.findall(r'\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}', content)\n83\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and len(dates) >= 2) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\n84\t\n85\t        has_status = bool(re.search(r'金叉|上方|golden|above', content))\n86\t        scores[\"monthly_status\"] = 1.0 if has_status else 0.0\n87\t\n88\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n89\t    has_daily = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\"daily\", \"日线\", \"day.*kline\"])\n90\t    has_weekly = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\"weekly\", \"周线\", \"week.*kline\"])\n91\t    has_monthly = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\"monthly\", \"月线\", \"month.*kline\"])\n92\t    scores[\"three_timeframes\"] = 1.0 if (has_daily and has_weekly and has_monthly) else (0.5 if (has_weekly or has_monthly) else 0.0)\n93\t    scores[\"three_ma_verified\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n94\t        [\"20周均线\", \"20月均线\", \"weekly.*ma20\", \"monthly.*ma\", \"20.*week\"]) else 0.0\n95\t\n96\t    return scores\n97\t```\n98\t\n99\t---\n100\t\n101\t## LLM Judge Rubric\n102\t\n103\t### Criterion 1: 三个时间维度的数据处理（Weight: 30%）\n104\t\n105\t**Score 1.0**: 正确分别获取日线、周线、月线K线数据，使用了不同的数据接口参数，三个维度均有足够预热长度，周线/月线数据非手动从日线聚合（或说明了聚合方法）。\n106\t**Score 0.75**: 获取了三种数据，但某一维度有聚合偏差或长度不足。\n107\t**Score 0.5**: 仅获取了日线和周线，月线用近似方法，或只